data.description: Nice home in an established Mimosa Heights area in Burkburnett. The living room features vaulted ceilings, wood burning fireplace and laminate flooring. The bedrooms are spacious and master bedroom includes two walk in closets. Master bath has dual sinks, shower and separate tub. Office is conveniently located off the kitchen and features French doors. Updates include carpets, HVAC and water heater (2021) main electrical panel box, fiber internet installed and money saving solar panels in 2022.
